fields.name: Bicep - Atlas
fields.description: Recorded in their new studio space, 'Atlas' is 6 minutes of unmistakable Bicep. With synth lines that ebb and flow across broken percussion and ethereal vocal snatches, the track was conceived as they toured their immense live-show across the globe.

fields.name: Tenderlonius - After the storm
fields.description: Tenderlonious returns with a brand new 4 track EP, seamlessly cooking up a blend of hybrid house and broken beat with his unique analogue productions and signature flute instrumentation.

fields.name: Mall Grab - How the dogs chill Vol1
fields.description: Producer & DJ Mall Grab has announced his new EP 'How The Dogs Chill, Vol. 1', on his brand new imprint 'Looking For Trouble'.

fields.name: Four Tet - Sixteen Oceans
fields.description: Wonderful new Four Tet album and perfect shutdown mellow soundtrack for the times. A fab follow up to the equally great New Energy.

fields.name: The Hacker and Various - Exit Planet Earth: Carbon
fields.description: Exit planet earth by 20/20 Vision is a new series of various artist vinyl releases, selected and compiled by Ralph Lawson.

fields.name: Henrik Schwarz - Together
fields.description: By using acoustic instruments as the source of his music, he creates freshly new electronic sounds through its treatment with digital interfaces.

fields.name: Derek Carr - Pursuit
fields.description: A long journey of 15 tracks that starts with some deep and dubby chords, acidic grooves and ends up with lush string based ambients.

fields.name: Laurent Garnier - Feelin Good
fields.description: Debuting on Rekids, Laurent Garnier & Chambray collaborate for a colossal single entitled Feelin' Good featuring two outstanding remixes from label owner Radio Slave.

fields.name: Big Fudge - Record Cleaner Kit
fields.description: Removes dust, dirt and fingerprints. Complete care system for your record collection.

fields.name: Ortofon Concorde MKII MIX
fields.description: The general purpose Ortofon Concorde MKII MIX Twin combines a pair of turntable cartridges, which boast solid performance and durability.

fields.name: Gorilla LP80 12 - LP Vinyl Record Storage Case

fields.name: UDG Starter 12 Inch Vinyl Record Bag 50
